| -------- | ---------- |
| \`scylla/maestro/errors.py\` | 100% |
| \`scylla/maestro/models.py\` | 100% |
| \`scylla/maestro/client.py\` | 96.6% |
| **Total** | **31 tests, 0 failures** |

